Package com.toy_store.java.utilities

Class CSVLine

java.lang.Object
com.toy_store.java.utilities.CSVLine
public class CSVLine
extends java.lang.Object
Class that represents a line in the CSV file containing the products. It's used as a separator between the CSV parser (CSVUtility) and the store.
